---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="機能 - Logipop">
	<section class="py-20 px-4">
		<div class="container mx-auto">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">機能紹介</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Logipopが提供する充実した機能で、効率的に論理的思考力を向上させることができます。
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-2">段階的学習プログラム</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">基礎から応用まで、レベルに応じた問題を順序立てて学習できます。</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-2">論理パターン分析</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">様々な論理パターンを分析し、思考の構造を理解できます。</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-2">進捗トラッキング</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">学習の進捗を詳細に記録し、成長を可視化します。</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-2">弱点分析</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">苦手な分野を特定し、重点的にトレーニングできます。</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-2">時間制限トレーニング</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">時間制限のある環境で、迅速な判断力を鍛えます。</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-2">詳細なフィードバック</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">各問題に対する詳細な解説とフィードバックを提供します。</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">さっそく始めてみませんか？</h2>
				<p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8">
					すべての機能を無料でお試しいただけます。
				</p>
				<a 
					href="/app" 
					class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 px-8"
				>
					無料で始める
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>